00:39:15.130 --> 00:39:18.020 align:middle line:84%
Now this is an interesting
piece of Greek history.

00:39:18.020 --> 00:39:22.329 align:middle line:84%
This should be mentioned when
you talk about Greek culture.

00:39:22.329 --> 00:39:24.405 align:middle line:90%
We talk about the Greeks.

