perspective on this reality,

00:40:28.450 --> 00:40:35.860 align:middle line:84%
or some alternative realities
normally invisible to us

00:40:35.860 --> 00:40:40.420 align:middle line:84%
when we are in the usual
state of consciousness.

00:40:40.420 --> 00:40:43.050 align:middle line:84%
So here would be the
different, yogas here

00:40:43.050 --> 00:40:47.940 align:middle line:84%
would be the different
techniques of Buddhism,

00:40:47.940 --> 00:40:51.500 align:middle line:84%
I already mentioned the
Taoist, the Sufi seekers,

00:40:51.500 --> 00:40:58.490 align:middle line:84%
the Christian meditation, Jesus
prayer, Kabbalistic exercises

00:40:58.490 --> 00:41:00.880 align:middle line:90%
and all those things.

00:41:00.880 --> 00:41:05.540 align:middle line:84%
So holotropic experiences
