00:41:05.540 --> 00:41:09.500 align:middle line:84%
prerequisite for any kind of
spiritual ritual practice.

00:41:09.500 --> 00:41:11.910 align:middle line:84%
We would not have
religions today

00:41:11.910 --> 00:41:14.810 align:middle line:84%
if it were not for these
