00:42:56.715 --> 00:43:01.150 align:middle line:84%
Now this is not a very
inspiring interpretation.

00:43:01.150 --> 00:43:05.620 align:middle line:84%
Our best, I wrote in the book
"The Cosmic Game," described

00:43:05.620 --> 00:43:08.350 align:middle line:84%
the very comprehensive
vision, alternative vision

00:43:08.350 --> 00:43:11.560 align:middle line:84%
of who we are in the
reality that is revealed

00:43:11.560 --> 00:43:13.610 align:middle line:90%
in these kinds of states.

00:43:13.610 --> 00:43:14.920 align:middle line:90%
And that people agree upon.

