00:43:17.245 --> 00:43:19.970 align:middle line:84%
they experience different
pieces of this kind

00:43:19.970 --> 00:43:23.055 align:middle line:90%
of a vision of reality.

00:43:23.055 --> 00:43:24.430 align:middle line:84%
They would agree
with each other.

00:43:24.430 --> 00:43:27.720 align:middle line:84%
They would sort of communicate
