00:43:27.720 --> 00:43:32.150 align:middle line:84%
Now our best model for the
brain now is the computer.

00:43:32.150 --> 00:43:35.300 align:middle line:84%
So to believe that there could
be some pathological process

00:43:35.300 --> 00:43:37.820 align:middle line:84%
