00:44:37.690 --> 00:44:40.890 align:middle line:84%
So this is an unbelievably
arrogant approach

00:44:40.890 --> 00:44:44.892 align:middle line:84%
to the spiritual and
ritual history of humanity.

00:44:44.892 --> 00:44:47.310 align:middle line:84%
It pathologizes
the spiritual life

00:44:47.310 --> 00:44:50.310 align:middle line:84%
of humanity, and to the
extent to which spirituality

00:44:50.310 --> 00:44:54.600 align:middle line:84%
and religion played an important
