(LAUGHTER)

00:46:18.510 --> 00:46:20.770 align:middle line:84%
There's a tremendous difference
between the worldview

00:46:20.770 --> 00:46:25.860 align:middle line:84%
of all pre-industrial cultures,
or ancient and native cultures,

00:46:25.860 --> 00:46:28.880 align:middle line:84%
on the one hand, and the
Western industrial civilization.

00:46:28.880 --> 00:46:31.740 align:middle line:90%
It is the official version.

00:46:31.740 --> 00:46:34.170 align:middle line:84%
There are obviously a lot of
people who don't share it,

00:46:34.170 --> 00:46:37.390 align:middle line:84%
and I think the
number is increasing.

00:46:37.390 --> 00:46:40.670 align:middle line:84%
Now a very obvious difference
is we know much more

00:46:40.670 --> 00:46:44.560 align:middle line:84%
about the details of
the material world,

00:46:44.560 --> 00:46:46.580 align:middle line:84%
about the microworld,
the macroworld,

00:46:46.580 --> 00:46:49.440 align:middle line:84%
and we can sort of use it to
apply it to technology and so

00:46:49.440 --> 00:46:50.359 align:middle line:90%
on.

00:46:50.359 --> 00:46:52.150 align:middle line:84%
But this is something
that you would expect

00:46:52.150 --> 00:46:56.270 align:middle line:84%
after 300 years of
experiments and sort

00:46:56.270 --> 00:47:00.490 align:middle line:84%
of sharing the information
through book print and so on.

00:47:00.490 --> 00:47:03.460 align:middle line:84%
But there's one difference
which is much more striking,

00:47:03.460 --> 00:47:06.950 align:middle line:84%
and that's in regard to
the spiritual dimension.

00:47:06.950 --> 00:47:10.580 align:middle line:84%
For all ancient and
pre-industrial cultures,

00:47:10.580 --> 00:47:12.290 align:middle line:90%
this was not the only reality.

00:47:12.290 --> 00:47:16.770 align:middle line:84%
There were also other
normally invisible dimensions

00:47:16.770 --> 00:47:21.170 align:middle line:84%
that were inhabited by
beings, by deities, by gods,

00:47:21.170 --> 00:47:24.960 align:middle line:84%
by discarnate entities, by
spirit guides, and so on.

00:47:24.960 --> 00:47:28.810 align:middle line:90%


00:47:28.810 --> 00:47:32.870 align:middle line:84%
When we die, this was
not the end of existence.

00:47:32.870 --> 00:47:35.680 align:middle line:84%
The idea was there was something
like the posthumous journey

00:47:35.680 --> 00:47:36.570 align:middle line:90%
of the soul.

00:47:36.570 --> 00:47:40.766 align:middle line:84%
That we're abouts of
the beyond, and so on.

00:47:40.766 --> 00:47:43.350 align:middle line:84%
In many cultures
independently, you

00:47:43.350 --> 00:47:46.180 align:middle line:90%
had the idea of reincarnation.

00:47:46.180 --> 00:47:49.110 align:middle line:84%
This is not the only
time we are here.

00:47:49.110 --> 00:47:50.560 align:middle line:90%
We have been here before.

00:47:50.560 --> 00:47:52.101 align:middle line:84%
We're going to come
back, and there's

00:47:52.101 --> 00:47:57.460 align:middle line:84%
some kind of link, karmic link
between those incarnations.

00:47:57.460 --> 00:48:01.450 align:middle line:84%
Now there is a diametrically
different opinion on that.

00:48:01.450 --> 00:48:03.600 align:middle line:84%
All these
pre-industrial cultures

00:48:03.600 --> 00:48:09.270 align:middle line:84%
agree that the world has
a spiritual dimension.

00:48:09.270 --> 00:48:12.590 align:middle line:84%
The official opinion of the
Western industrial civilization

00:48:12.590 --> 00:48:13.600 align:middle line:90%
is this is nonsense.

00:48:13.600 --> 00:48:15.030 align:middle line:90%
These are fairy tales.

00:48:15.030 --> 00:48:17.430 align:middle line:84%
These guys didn't
have decent science.

00:48:17.430 --> 00:48:23.100 align:middle line:84%
They were into superstition,
primitive, magical thinking.

00:48:23.100 --> 00:48:25.970 align:middle line:84%
Now if somebody from a strictly
psychiatric perspective,

00:48:25.970 --> 00:48:31.000 align:middle line:84%
if somebody takes mysticism
and spirituality seriously,

00:48:31.000 --> 00:48:33.680 align:middle line:84%
and they are intelligent,
you can't blame them,

00:48:33.680 --> 00:48:35.810 align:middle line:84%
not knowing about
Western science,

00:48:35.810 --> 00:48:40.540 align:middle line:84%
then we have psychoanalysis that
tells us, if that's the case,

00:48:40.540 --> 00:48:42.360 align:middle line:84%
then you have a
hangup from childhood.

00:48:42.360 --> 00:48:45.790 align:middle line:84%
You're carrying around infantile
images of your parents.

00:48:45.790 --> 00:48:47.800 align:middle line:84%
And you're projecting
it out there

00:48:47.800 --> 00:48:51.120 align:middle line:84%
and making gods and
goddesses out of them.

00:48:51.120 --> 00:48:52.670 align:middle line:84%
And if you have
direct experiences

00:48:52.670 --> 00:48:55.100 align:middle line:84%
of these other realities,
you get a diagnosis,

00:48:55.100 --> 00:48:59.570 align:middle line:84%
you're put on tranquilizers,
and you're hospitalized.

00:48:59.570 --> 00:49:04.000 align:middle line:84%
Now the official opinion again
about the difference in the two

00:49:04.000 --> 00:49:08.370 align:middle line:84%
perspectives is that it
reflects the superiority

00:49:08.370 --> 00:49:09.595 align:middle line:90%
of Western science.

00:49:09.595 --> 00:49:12.170 align:middle line:90%


00:49:12.170 --> 00:49:14.990 align:middle line:84%
Now the kind of
conclusion I've come to,

00:49:14.990 --> 00:49:16.920 align:middle line:84%
and I think many
of my colleagues

00:49:16.920 --> 00:49:19.270 align:middle line:84%
who are doing
consciousness research

00:49:19.270 --> 00:49:21.080 align:middle line:84%
and had some
personal experiences

00:49:21.080 --> 00:49:25.440 align:middle line:84%
of these holotropic states,
is that the explanation

00:49:25.440 --> 00:49:28.470 align:middle line:84%
is somewhat
different, and that is

00:49:28.470 --> 00:49:31.200 align:middle line:84%
that this difference
reflects naivete

00:49:31.200 --> 00:49:33.950 align:middle line:84%
of the Western industrial
civilization in relation

00:49:33.950 --> 00:49:36.070 align:middle line:90%
to the holotropic states.

00:49:36.070 --> 00:49:38.120 align:middle line:84%
What these other
cultures had that we

00:49:38.120 --> 00:49:45.070 align:middle line:84%
don't have were systematic, was
systematic use of technologies

00:49:45.070 --> 00:49:48.580 align:middle line:84%
of using these experiences,
and during their lifetimes,

00:49:48.580 --> 00:49:52.920 align:middle line:84%
they had repeated opportunities
to have those experiences.

00:49:52.920 --> 00:49:54.830 align:middle line:84%
And when you have
those experiences,

00:49:54.830 --> 00:49:58.640 align:middle line:84%
you have to include them
into your worldview.

00:49:58.640 --> 00:50:00.710 align:middle line:84%
I've worked with
hundreds of people

00:50:00.710 --> 00:50:03.000 align:middle line:84%
in the Western
civilization, in Europe

00:50:03.000 --> 00:50:05.730 align:middle line:84%
and here, who had all
the best education

00:50:05.730 --> 00:50:10.090 align:middle line:84%
you can imagine--
university studies, IQ,

00:50:10.090 --> 00:50:12.380 align:middle line:90%
trained in various disciplines.

00:50:12.380 --> 00:50:15.780 align:middle line:84%
When they had the opportunity
